{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01EoaePjA5tN2cd6kduq4Dmb","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze the impact of the gRPC-Go metadata context separation change on the etcd codebase. I need to:\n\n1. Find what changed in grpc-go/metadata/metadata.go\n2. Find all etcd files using the old API\n3. Identify transitive metadata forwarding patterns\n4. Classify breakage types\n\nLet me use Sourcegraph MCP tools to find this information.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2112,"cache_read_input_tokens":14236,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2112},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9c6a61d1-0fa0-43c6-80f7-1a961d909727","uuid":"97af57c0-5cee-4a48-9f8c-b673d0b032ee"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01EoaePjA5tN2cd6kduq4Dmb","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01XckfNxaFSdevMqaooMrtgP","name":"Agent","input":{"description":"Analyze gRPC metadata API changes and etcd impact","subagent_type":"general-purpose","prompt":"\nAnalyze the impact of the gRPC-Go metadata context separation change on the etcd codebase.\n\n## Tasks\n\n### 1. Find the grpc-go PR #1157 changes in metadata.go\nUse `mcp__sourcegraph__read_file` to read the current grpc-go metadata package:\n- Repo: `github.com/grpc/grpc-go`\n- File: `metadata/metadata.go`\n\nAlso use `mcp__sourcegraph__commit_search` or `mcp__sourcegraph__diff_search` to find the changes from PR #1157 in grpc-go. Try searching for commits related to \"metadata FromIncomingContext\" or \"metadata context separation\".\n\n### 2. Find all etcd files using old grpc metadata API\nUse `mcp__sourcegraph__keyword_search` to find all files in etcd repos that use:\n- `metadata.FromContext`\n- `metadata.NewContext`\n- `metadata.FromIncomingContext`\n- `metadata.FromOutgoingContext`\n- `metadata.NewOutgoingContext`\n\nSearch in: `github.com/etcd-io/etcd` or `github.com/coreos/etcd`\n\n### 3. For each affected file, determine:\n- Which old API functions it uses\n- Whether it's doing metadata forwarding (reading incoming metadata and adding to outgoing context - this is the most dangerous pattern)\n- Breakage type: compile error (old function removed) vs runtime (silent metadata drop)\n\n## MCP Tool Usage\nUse these tools:\n- `mcp__sourcegraph__read_file` with `{\"repo\": \"github.com/grpc/grpc-go\", \"file_path\": \"metadata/metadata.go\"}` (no revision needed for latest)\n- `mcp__sourcegraph__keyword_search` with `{\"query\": \"metadata.FromContext repo:github.com/etcd-io/etcd\"}`\n- `mcp__sourcegraph__keyword_search` with `{\"query\": \"metadata.NewContext repo:github.com/etcd-io/etcd\"}`\n- `mcp__sourcegraph__diff_search` or `mcp__sourcegraph__commit_search` to find the PR #1157 changes\n\n## Output\nReturn a comprehensive JSON structure with:\n```json\n{\n  \"api_changes\": {\n    \"removed\": [\"list of removed/renamed functions with signatures\"],\n    \"added\": [\"new replacement functions with signatures\"],\n    \"description\": \"summary of the breaking change\"\n  },\n  \"affected_files\": [\n    {\n      \"path\": \"relative/path/in/etcd\",\n      \"repo\": \"full repo path\",\n      \"old_api_uses\": [\"metadata.FromContext\", etc],\n      \"breakage_type\": \"compile_error|runtime_behavior|deprecation\",\n      \"is_metadata_forwarding\": true/false,\n      \"forwarding_pattern\": \"description if forwarding\",\n      \"severity\": \"critical|high|medium|low\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"critical_forwarding_files\": [\"list of files doing metadata forwarding\"],\n  \"summary\": {\n    \"total_affected\": N,\n    \"compile_errors\": N,\n    \"runtime_behavior_changes\": N,\n    \"critical_forwarding\": N\n  }\n}\n```\n\nBe thorough - missing files means incomplete impact analysis. Search multiple etcd repos (etcd-io/etcd, coreos/etcd).\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2112,"cache_read_input_tokens":14236,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2112},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9c6a61d1-0fa0-43c6-80f7-1a961d909727","uuid":"e0166612-336b-418e-a232-803272f8bb74"}
{"type":"system","subtype":"task_started","task_id":"a2aa17c397b5ff39d","tool_use_id":"toolu_01XckfNxaFSdevMqaooMrtgP","description":"Analyze gRPC metadata API changes and etcd impact","task_type":"local_agent","prompt":"\nAnalyze the impact of the gRPC-Go metadata context separation change on the etcd codebase.\n\n## Tasks\n\n### 1. Find the grpc-go PR #1157 changes in metadata.go\nUse `mcp__sourcegraph__read_file` to read the current grpc-go metadata package:\n- Repo: `github.com/grpc/grpc-go`\n- File: `metadata/metadata.go`\n\nAlso use `mcp__sourcegraph__commit_search` or `mcp__sourcegraph__diff_search` to find the changes from PR #1157 in grpc-go. Try searching for commits related to \"metadata FromIncomingContext\" or \"metadata context separation\".\n\n### 2. Find all etcd files using old grpc metadata API\nUse `mcp__sourcegraph__keyword_search` to find all files in etcd repos that use:\n- `metadata.FromContext`\n- `metadata.NewContext`\n- `metadata.FromIncomingContext`\n- `metadata.FromOutgoingContext`\n- `metadata.NewOutgoingContext`\n\nSearch in: `github.com/etcd-io/etcd` or `github.com/coreos/etcd`\n\n### 3. For each affected file, determine:\n- Which old API functions it uses\n- Whether it's doing metadata forwarding (reading incoming metadata and adding to outgoing context - this is the most dangerous pattern)\n- Breakage type: compile error (old function removed) vs runtime (silent metadata drop)\n\n## MCP Tool Usage\nUse these tools:\n- `mcp__sourcegraph__read_file` with `{\"repo\": \"github.com/grpc/grpc-go\", \"file_path\": \"metadata/metadata.go\"}` (no revision needed for latest)\n- `mcp__sourcegraph__keyword_search` with `{\"query\": \"metadata.FromContext repo:github.com/etcd-io/etcd\"}`\n- `mcp__sourcegraph__keyword_search` with `{\"query\": \"metadata.NewContext repo:github.com/etcd-io/etcd\"}`\n- `mcp__sourcegraph__diff_search` or `mcp__sourcegraph__commit_search` to find the PR #1157 changes\n\n## Output\nReturn a comprehensive JSON structure with:\n```json\n{\n  \"api_changes\": {\n    \"removed\": [\"list of removed/renamed functions with signatures\"],\n    \"added\": [\"new replacement functions with signatures\"],\n    \"description\": \"summary of the breaking change\"\n  },\n  \"affected_files\": [\n    {\n      \"path\": \"relative/path/in/etcd\",\n      \"repo\": \"full repo path\",\n      \"old_api_uses\": [\"metadata.FromContext\", etc],\n      \"breakage_type\": \"compile_error|runtime_behavior|deprecation\",\n      \"is_metadata_forwarding\": true/false,\n      \"forwarding_pattern\": \"description if forwarding\",\n      \"severity\": \"critical|high|medium|low\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"critical_forwarding_files\": [\"list of files doing metadata forwarding\"],\n  \"summary\": {\n    \"total_affected\": N,\n    \"compile_errors\": N,\n    \"runtime_behavior_changes\": N,\n    \"critical_forwarding\": N\n  }\n}\n```\n\nBe thorough - missing files means incomplete impact analysis. Search multiple etcd repos (etcd-io/etcd, coreos/etcd).\n","uuid":"38fa34c9-f3b7-468f-a57d-a82a669aa2fc","session_id":"9c6a61d1-0fa0-43c6-80f7-1a961d909727"}
